languages.text: Под полом можно разглядеть остатки системы жизнеобеспечения пустотного корабля — похоже, их просто решили не демонтировать при разборе судна.
Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.
languages.original_text: Под полом можно разглядеть остатки системы жизнеобеспечения пустотного корабля — похоже, их просто решили не демонтировать при разборе судна.

traits.locale_text: Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.

languages.text: 在地板下面，你看到了虚空舰生命维持系统的残骸。看来，当初拆掉了这艘船的人，决定把这些东西留在原处。
languages.original_text: Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.

traits.locale_text: 在地板下面，你看到了虚空舰生命维持系统的残骸。看来，当初拆掉了这艘船的人，决定把这些东西留在原处。

languages.text: Bajo el suelo, distingues los restos del sistema de soporte vital de la nave del vacío. Parece que, sea quien sea el que la desmontó, decidió dejarla como estaba.
languages.original_text: Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.

traits.locale_text: Bajo el suelo, distingues los restos del sistema de soporte vital de la nave del vacío. Parece que, sea quien sea el que la desmontó, decidió dejarla como estaba.

languages.text: 床下にはヴォイドシップの生命維持装置の残骸が見える。この船を解体したものがそのままにしておいたのだろう。
languages.original_text: Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.

traits.locale_text: 床下にはヴォイドシップの生命維持装置の残骸が見える。この船を解体したものがそのままにしておいたのだろう。

languages.text: Unter dem Boden siehst du die Überreste des Lebenserhaltungssystems des Raumschiffs – wer immer die Demontage durchgeführt hat, war wohl der Ansicht, es einfach zu belassen, wo es war.
languages.original_text: Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.

traits.locale_text: Unter dem Boden siehst du die Überreste des Lebenserhaltungssystems des Raumschiffs – wer immer die Demontage durchgeführt hat, war wohl der Ansicht, es einfach zu belassen, wo es war.

languages.text: Sous le sol, vous apercevez les vestiges du système de survie du vaisseau. Ceux qui ont démantelé le navire ont manifestement renoncé à y toucher.
languages.original_text: Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.

traits.locale_text: Sous le sol, vous apercevez les vestiges du système de survie du vaisseau. Ceux qui ont démantelé le navire ont manifestement renoncé à y toucher.

languages.text: Zeminin altında, uçsuz gemisinin yaşam destek sisteminden geriye kalanları görebiliyorsun. Bu gemiyi demonte edenler, sistemi yerinde bırakmaya karar vermiş gibi.
languages.original_text: Under the floor, you can see the remains of the voidship's life support system — it seems that whoever dismantled the vessel decided just to leave it in place.

traits.locale_text: Zeminin altında uçsuz gemisinin yaşam destek sisteminden geriye kalanları görebiliyorsun. Görünüşe bakılırsa, bu gemiyi demonte edenler sistemi yerinde bırakmaya karar vermiş.
